data.description: Don’t wait to see this BEAUTIFUL home in Wetumpka! With 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 baths, a screened in porch and an amazing saltwater pool with a cabana…you will never want to leave home. The open floorplan makes entertaining and daily living so nice. You’ll love the warm tongue-and-groove wood ceiling in the Den and the coffered ceiling in the formal Dining Room. The Kitchen features stainless appliances (including a gas range), plenty of cabinets and counterspace, undermount cabinet lighting, a double stainless-steel sink, and a convenient breakfast bar. The large Breakfast Room has a built-in cushioned banquette and a wall of windows so you can enjoy the view of the fully fenced backyard, lighted grilling pavilion, and gorgeous pool. The Main Bedroom has wood floors and a luxurious en-suite Bath. The Main Bath boasts two separate vanities, a large two-headed shower with custom tile, a deep garden tub, a private water closet, and two walk-in closets. The 3 guest rooms are located on the opposite side of the home providing extra privacy. They share the 2nd full Bath located in the hall. The laundry room has built-in cabinets providing extra storage and there is a perfect built-in drop zone and bench as you enter the home from the 2-car garage. The backyard is where everyone will want to be! The pool is fenced separately and there is so much room for entertaining or just relaxing with your family. Call today for your showing!
